        <title>Description and Operation</title>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Battery and Cables</title>
            <para>This vehicle is equipped with a primary and secondary 12-volt maintenance-free battery.</para>
            <para>The battery and cable system consists of the following components:</para>
            <randlist type="bullet">
                <item>
                    <para>Primary battery</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Secondary battery</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Battery cable assembly</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Battery tray</para>
                </item>
            </randlist>
            <para>International Truck and Engine Corporation strongly recommends that lead-acid batteries be returned to
                an authorized recycling facility for disposal.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
    </svcproc>
